Readme File:
***********************************
Counter Strike:Source
***********************************
TITLE: gg_desert_battle
AUTHOR: Zaennon_
E-MAIL: askurflint@hotmail.com

FILENAME: gg_desert_battle.bsp
FILESIZE: 780 kB
DATE RELEASED: 21 December 2008

INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS: Place the gg_desert_battle.bsp in "\Steam\steamapps\[username]\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps" folder, run the game and create server!

DESCRIPTION:
I made this gungame map mainly for turbo deathmatch mode.
Supports up to 32 players.
Enjoy!

BUGS: For the moment there are no known bugs, but if you notice anything please e-mail me so i can fix it.
